data.text:
Hello,

Please check the screenshot:

https://prnt.sc/-MZnBd_YhBzK

On woocommerce site, we allow users to upload image reviews, and it issue: Could not retrieve file path to lost of images, but not all of them.

We are also using a plugin of offload image to Digitalocean Space cloud storage, and please check it at https://wordpress.org/plugins/amazon-s3-and-cloudfront/.

In this case, the issue will cause those images will not to be offloaded to cloud storage.

Would you please let us know how to fix, please?

Thanks
